Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:26.83,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:32.95,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:39.14,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:45.59,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:48.96,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:52.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:58.54,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:08.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:14.31,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.51,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:23.86,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:29.14,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.E.70年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「血色情人节」的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致地球与PLANT的紧张关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终升级为武力冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战前无人怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军将以数量优势取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现实出乎所有人的预料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战局陷入拉锯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转眼间 第十一个月即将过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩草就要除根
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型战舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有干掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:00:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在卫星里？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:37.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1175,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}分崩离析的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过港区 进入卫星内部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曙光社损失严重 强袭启动中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避 右转舵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相转移装甲 来尝尝这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 强化穿甲弹也没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰尾导弹发射管 7到10号发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 敌机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光制导
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住 千万别击中主轴和地表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开…开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么强劲的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然装配给机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机动战士撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整相对速度 注意重力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五程序班待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界面上线 开始数据传输
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防火墙抗体注入完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接数据库 剩余300毫秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班 注意能量包极化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心动了你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外装点检和充电已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真佩服他们 还在用这样的OS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁泽长机返航 机体中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防班 救护班 B甲板待命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长机的胳膊被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对手是他的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基露露少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴看到你平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你们保住大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得太及时了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还是个孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那孩子在驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯上尉 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 真没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军 第七轨道舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆·拉·弗拉戈上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二宇域 第五特务师团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫·拉米亚斯上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同属 娜塔尔·巴基露露少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想搞张登舰许可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这船上谁负责？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长及主要军官全部战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 当前负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应为拉米亚斯上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸存的只有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰上的下级士官和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其余十几人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在主轴室里 侥幸逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长他们… 战死？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这算啥事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…先给个许可吧 拉米亚斯上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我来的船也沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 那边是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 是平民的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来袭时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不知何故出现在厂区
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带他上了「G」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫 基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏他的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还击退了一台Ginn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保住了这唯一的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击退了Ginn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是送那些新兵蛋子来开这东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸当时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在司令室报到 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 调整人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在米歇尔带回了这段影像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我如何辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被地球军机动战士击伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会成为别人笑柄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于原配OS的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们最了解不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这台机体如此生猛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在唯一明确的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能把它留在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如无法捕获 就在这里摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括战舰在内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次切忌轻敌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔和奥罗尔立即做好出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D装备的使用许可已经下达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不要给他们留下机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿迪斯舰长 请允许让我出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有机体了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且你已经
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了抢夺机体的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就谦让一下吧 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔他们的懊悔不比你少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人怎么了 基拉不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你们都瞎了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在过河拆桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把枪收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯上尉 这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要这么大惊小怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫利奥波利斯是座中立国的殖民卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了躲避战火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有调整人移居此处也不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一代调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一代？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母都是自然人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 不好意思哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家紧张兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想问清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈上尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没少看那些驾驶员们的模拟战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们做个动作都得用上吃奶的劲儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差距啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉 你去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的机体还躺在机库
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面克鲁泽还等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可难缠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换成我是你们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会在这里聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6号集装箱 Ginn装备D装
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始前01:00
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击机体前往甲板待命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是上D装
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备打要塞攻略战吗 克鲁泽队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样赫利奥波利斯就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:10:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作孽不可活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号称什么中立国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有从曙光社运来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先确保强袭的弹药和补给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛多克中士 快来这边看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候还睡得着也是种本事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是累的 基拉辛苦到现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么话就直说 卡兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对基拉来说那种事也就是「辛苦」一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉说 他改写了那机器的OS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候改的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉不可能事先看过那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他是什么时候改OS的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道基拉是个调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想想 对改造基因的调整人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事辛苦一下就做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特军个个都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军能打赢那帮家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 卫星里的避难情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经基本达到百分之百
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可刚才那下 让警报等级升到9级了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防空洞被完全锁上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那群小鬼怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔他们下船也无处可去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们因为目击军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拉米亚斯上尉逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以随意放走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那让他们陪着咱们突围？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一出这里 外面可就是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为强袭的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打算让它参加实战？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不利用的话 谈何突围？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子点头了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次让弗拉戈上尉驾驶如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别难为我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么开得了那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子改写的OS参数 看过没？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人谁用得了那玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不能把贵重的机体交给一个平民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就傻傻地跑出去当靶子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥罗尔出击完成 米歇尔上弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架也出击 怎么没听说？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 阿斯兰·萨拉开着夺来的机体？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上命他返航
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据的抽取已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也许更加有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看地球机动战士之间的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星全域电波受扰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中子干扰数值上升
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不等我们出去就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个死鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又打算在赫利奥波利斯里开战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们没法开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可以放开了打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我们继续卷入战争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许没说错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的世界在打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我们正是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为讨厌战争 才选择了这个中立国
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯上尉 拉米亚斯上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请速来舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上来指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先当上尉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你比我熟悉这船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 大天使号准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉的机动堡垒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 躺着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 麻烦弗拉戈上尉负责CIC
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有战斗找上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警报等级9级
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放你们下船也是送死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有闯过这关 离开赫利奥波利斯后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后想说这艘船上 只有那一架机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只有我能驾驶对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先从赫利奥波利斯突围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中尽可能避免伤及卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号集装箱 剑袭者装备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑袭者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不会发生那种事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现接近的热源1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热纹谱 是Ginn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是攻击据点用的重型装备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打算炸平这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞区另有一队敌人入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让强袭出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一架是X-303 神盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就投入实战了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它现在是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死在它手上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科林斯飞弹 准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光制导 精确瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实弹对相转移装甲无效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮 激光联动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦点扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥罗尔和纳修负责战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来了就让我看看你的志气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 那边屏幕能看到外面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他继续破坏卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四号军械库中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔离处理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拦截
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及
